-- variants: reflect a union's variant descriptors.
-- Run-only demo: the result embeds `Type` values (see docs/spec/09-metaprogramming
-- /reflection.md), so `check`/`compile` refuse it as a program entry result
-- (S4 entry-type gate); the lenient interpreter still shows it under `run`.
-- Usage: zutai-cli run examples/macro_kernel/reflection/variants_union.zt

Result :: type { #ok : { value : Text; }; #done; };
variants Result
